     IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.                              
     PROGRAM-ID.    REFMODPG.                              
     AUTHOR.        MANASA.                                
     INSTALLATION.  IBM E&T.                               
     DATE-WRITTEN.  8/17/17.                               
     DATE-COMPILED.                                        
     SECURITY.      NONE.                                  
  ******************************************************   
  * MY SECOND PROGRAM                                      
  ******************************************************   
     ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                 
     DATA DIVISION.                                        
     WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                              
   01   WS-WHOLE-NAME PIC X(30) VALUE "NAGA MANASA VALLI". 
   01   WS-FIRST-NAME PIC X(4).                            
     01   WS-MIDDLE-NAME PIC X(8).                         
  01   WS-LAST-NAME PIC X(5).                           
    PROCEDURE DIVISION.                                 
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME TO WS-FIRST-NAME.          
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME TO WS-MIDDLE-NAME.         
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME TO WS-LAST-NAME.           
          DISPLAY WS-FIRST-NAME.                        
          DISPLAY WS-MIDDLE-NAME.                       
          DISPLAY WS-LAST-NAME.                         
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME (1:4) TO WS-FIRST-NAME.    
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME (6:6) TO WS-MIDDLE-NAME.   
          MOVE WS-WHOLE-NAME (13:) TO WS-LAST-NAME.     
          DISPLAY WS-FIRST-NAME.                        
          DISPLAY WS-MIDDLE-NAME.                       
          DISPLAY WS-LAST-NAME.                         
          STOP  RUN.                                    
